  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The shaman can touch a willing creature as a standard action to remove one of the following conditions: fatigued, shaken, or sickened.</p>\n<p>At 8th level, she adds confused and frightened to the list of conditions she can remove.</p>\n<p>At 12th level, she also adds dazed, nauseated, and panicked.</p>\n<p>The shaman can use this ability a number of times per day equal to her shaman level.</p>"
